snippet.title: Finding Frankie - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
#FindingFrankie #FindingFrankieTrailer
Wishlist the game on Steam Now: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2597970/Finding_Frankie/
RELEASING OCTOBER 25TH!

Finding Frankie is our upcoming single-player horror game that throws you into Frankie's maniacal twisted horrific game show! This game requires not just running, but vaulting, rail-grinding, sliding, trampoline jumping and more! Will you make it to the grand prize at the end of this horrific horror game-show, or will you become just another elimination?

Finding Frankie has no shortage of jumpscares, scares, scary moments, and terrifying monsters, but it also has some of the most intense parkour you'll ever see as you navigate throughout the world's biggest indoor trampoline and parkour park.

This game while taking inspiration from other horror game titles such as Five Nights at Freddy's/FNaF, Poppy Playtime, Bendy and the Ink Machine and more, hopes to start it a new wave of parkour themed horror experiences!

#FindingFrankie #FindingFrankieGame #FindingFrankieTrailer
